data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Section rhythm: contained photo hero, material cards, service accordion with roofer image, drone-backed proof/process, projects teaser, FAQ, quote CTA, and a quiet oversized-wordmark footer. Tokens will map to the roofing contract: charcoal primary, slate secondary, moss action, off-white bands, Inter-style sans throughout as required by the active brand kit."}

